  "keyFeatures": [
    "Google Gemini-powered AI audit with 4-dimensional analysis",
    "Gutenberg Answer Card block for AI answer engines",
    "Comprehensive schema markup support (Article, FAQ, HowTo, Product, LocalBusiness)",
    "SEO essentials: meta titles, descriptions, social cards, XML sitemaps",
    "AI crawler control for PerplexityBot, GPTBot, CCBot, and anthropic-ai",
    "Compatibility mode with Yoast, Rank Math, SEOPress, and All in One SEO",
    "Breadcrumbs with BreadcrumbList schema",
    "301/302 redirect manager with wildcard support",
    "404 monitor with retention controls",
    "WP-CLI commands for bulk audits",
    "Encrypted API key storage with libsodium",
    "Editor sidebar panel for in-editor SEO workflow"
  ],
